        "class": "",
        "text": ").",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Altars for incense.—Ha-mĕqattĕrôth—literally, the incense-burners. The term occurs here only.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Altars for incense.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "Ha-mĕqattĕrôth",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—literally, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "the incense-burners.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " The term occurs here only.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Cast them into the brook Kidron.—See on 2Chronicles 29:16. Thus the city was purified as well as the Temple.",
